The '''''Al-Hadath''' ({{lang-ar|'''الحدث'''}})'' is an Arabic weekly newspaper in [[Amman]], [[Jordan]].<ref>{{cite book|author=Egbert Harmsen|title=Islam, Civil Society and Social Work: Muslim Voluntary Welfare Associations in Jordan Between Patronage and Empowerment|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wiC6QghEH38C&pg=PA161|accessdate=7 September 2016|year=2008|publisher=Amsterdam University Press|isbn=978-90-5356-995-5|page=161}}</ref> The name "Al-Hadath" can be roughly translated as "the event".
